{"tid":1962123,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"呢隻腦魔值幾多分","createTime":"2020-04-07T09:13:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-08T09:20:02.000Z","uid":209106,"like":83,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"d5a837b8ee3dae4e29bad26d6a9bd4d73ff4a675","tid":1962123,"uid":209106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T09:13:14.000Z","msg":"買咗啲羊毛diy諗住整下啲公仔俾女朋友當禮物<br />\n<br />\n整整吓突然間想自己玩下，第一隻都未整完就走咗去挑戰腦魔<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6jBbgR9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6jBbgR9.png&h=6e663785&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n塑型先<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CJFWsYU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCJFWsYU.png&h=c2bb77c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n0秒即棄，裙邊算<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V48UeD0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV48UeD0.png&h=1a9b448a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢啲9毛飛晒出嚟唔知點搞<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9hAb1i4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9hAb1i4.png&h=ac5b5919&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n個口好難整黑色好容易撈埋其他毛<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DKTMQcv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDKTMQcv.png&h=51d417bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n成個弱智兒童咁<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TEG27Zf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTEG27Zf.png&h=f90c8dcf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n加返幾條鳩毛俾佢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後加加埋埋整咗四個幾鐘，跟住我阿妹入咗嚟話呢隻野咁核突嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望女朋友唔係咁諗"},{"pid":"27feea42f4ac5adb55cb4653402dfda75dba74be","tid":1962123,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T09:14:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f15910ba1c6893d0477a7d8e24f82189e